OL,3,CTwo officers injured following 'chase
OL,4,Cinvolving chainsaw'
OL,6,FTwo officers have been injured and a
OL,7,Fman arrested after footage emerged
OL,8,Fonline of police being chased by a man
OL,9,F"carrying a chainsaw" near Glasgow.
OL,11,FOfficers attended the scene of a
OL,12,Fdisturbance involving a weapon on
OL,13,FGlasgow Road in Paisley at around 1pm
OL,14,Fon Monday, following a collision
OL,15,Fbetween a car and a stationary police
OL,16,Fvehicle.
