OL,6,FFootage widely shared on social media
OL,7,Fshowed a man running with a weapon `
OL,8,Fwhich appeared to be a chainsaw `
OL,9,Fmoments after an officer was seen
OL,10,Frunning.
OL,12,FTwo officers were treated by
OL,13,Fparamedics for injuries and a 30-year-
OL,14,Fold man was arrested in connection
OL,15,Fwith the incident.
OL,17,FPolice said there is no wider risk to
OL,18,Fthe public and officers remain at the
OL,19,Fscene while enquires are ongoing.
