OL,6,FA police statement said: "Around 1pm
OL,7,Fon Monday, May 6, 2024, a disturbance
OL,8,Finvolving a weapon occurred following
OL,9,Fa collision involving a car and a
OL,10,Fstationary police vehicle on Glasgow
OL,11,FRoad in Paisley.
OL,13,F"Two officers were injured and were
OL,14,Ftreated by paramedics. A 30-year-old
OL,15,Fman was arrested in connection with
OL,16,Fthe incident.
OL,18,F"There is no wider risk to the public
OL,19,Fand officers remain at the scene while
OL,20,Finquiries are ongoing."
